                            <comment id="205601" author="jgmitter" created="Thu, 17 Aug 2017 12:35:43 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This problem is due to the style/customstyle_fo.xsl logic for handling of the condition attribute on section tags.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
